column2: SELECT  a.NYU_num, c.objID, c.plate, c.fiberID, c.mjd, c.specObjID FROM MyDB.VAGC_spectro_position a, MyDB.VAGC_spectro_PFM b, SpecPhotoAll c WHERE a.sdss_spectro_position=b.SDSS_SPECTRO_POSITION and c.plate=b.PLATE and c.fiberID=b.FIBER and c.mjd=b.MJD and c.objID IS NOT null   INTO VAGC_photoobjid_nonull
